            "title": "Craftsmanship & Quality",
            "description": "Skilled artisans with decades of experience.|Premium materials sourced globally.|Precision engineering meets traditional craftsmanship.|Every detail inspected before shipping."
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "accordion_item",
